DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this study is to determine if Perlane-L is safe in increasing cheek volume.
DOC.brief_title: Efficacy and Safety of Perlane-L in the Correction of Midface Volume Deficit
DOC.criteria: Loss of Fullness in Midface Area Other items as identified in the protocol History of allergy or hypersensitivity to injectable hyaluronic acid gel or lidocaine. Other items as identified in the protocol
